title: Discord Server for everyone! [EUW] [ German , English ] Trying to build a nice Community

embed.title: Discord - Free voice and text chat for gamers
embed.description: Step up your game with a modern voice & text chat app. Crystal clear voice, multiple server and channel support, mobile apps, and more. Get your free server now!

body:
Hello Guys , I'm from Germany and 21 Years old. I'm Trying to build my own Discord Server. Feel free to join and we can spent time together. We could play Normal League Games, Aram & much more!
If you Interested to join my club [WeWet] feel free to ask. Currently we have 20 Clan Members.
